# --- Environment Variables for step-ca Portainer Stack (Synology Reverse Proxy) ---

# 1. Host Path Configuration
# The absolute path on your Synology where your 'intermediate-ca' folder is located.
STEP_CA_HOST_PATH=/volume1/docker/step-ca

# 2. Network Configuration
# The external port on the Synology host to map to the container's internal port 9443.
# We use 9444 to avoid conflict with Portainer. This port is now ESSENTIAL.
STEP_CA_PORT=9444

# 3. Docker Secrets Configuration
# The name of the Docker Secret created in Portainer to hold your CA password.
CA_PASSWORD_SECRET_NAME=step_ca_password```

